trans-unit.source: Sokoban is a puzzle game that puts the player in the shoes of a handler in an unreasonably crowded and quirky warehouse.
trans-unit.target: Sokoban is a puzzle game that puts the player in the shoes of a handler in an unreasonably crowded and quirky warehouse.

trans-unit.source: The player can move his character and push buckets. He cannot walk through walls or buckets.
trans-unit.target: The player can move his character and push buckets. He cannot walk through walls or buckets.

trans-unit.source: The goal is to get each bucket on a target cell.
trans-unit.target: The goal is to get each bucket on a target cell.

trans-unit.source: If a bucket is found to be on a moving walkway, it will be moved in the direction indicated by the moving walkway.
trans-unit.target: If a bucket is found to be on a moving walkway, it will be moved in the direction indicated by the moving walkway.

trans-unit.source: If any obstacle is found to be on the cell where a bucket should be moved, the bucket won't move as long as the cell won't have been freed.
trans-unit.target: If any obstacle is found to be on the cell where a bucket should be moved, the bucket won't move as long as the cell won't have been freed.

trans-unit.source: Try to complete each level by making the least moves possibles in order to score more !
trans-unit.target: Try to complete each level by making the least moves possibles in order to score more !
